| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2711 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3dc4cc01-d7a3-50c8-a5ff-7bf72e2fdb00"
